Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hyakkaou Private Academy}Học viện tư Hyakkaou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Approaching its 122th anniversary,}Kỉ niệm 122 năm thành lập,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{this academy is known for tradition and status.}là học viện với nhiều truyền thống và lâu đời.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Showdown!}Hạ bài!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Fullhouse!}Cù lũ!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Too bad!}Quá tiếc!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you for the game.}Chơi vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ro-}T-Thùng
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{Royal Straight Flush!?}Thùng phá sảnh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, you've been through a lot today.}Cậu cũng cố hết sức rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{But keep your spirits up, 'kay?}Nhưng vẫn còn kém lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Fi-}Chó
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ngoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Starting today,}Từ hôm đó,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm no longer "human".}tôi không còn là "Con người" nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Those are the rules of this academy.}Đó là luật lệ ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Money is everything here.}Tiền là tất cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{And so,}Và,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{The strength lies within gambling.}bài bạc là sức mạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Got a straight.}Sảnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ugh, you win again, Saotome.}Lại là Saotome nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Same as usual, Mary-chan!}Vẫn mạnh như thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{So good!}Quá mạnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Seems like today is not your day.}Hôm nay tôi không khỏe đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{I am...}Mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{a house pet now.}là chó cưng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Regaining your status is near impossible.}Quay trở lại con người là điều không thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Or so I thought...}Hay mình nghĩ thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Until she appeared.}Cho đến khi cô ấy xuất hiện.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's start today with introducing a new transfer student.}Bắt đầu để cô giới thiệu học sinh mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you, everyone. My name is Yumeko Jabami.}Rất vui được gặp mọi người, mình là Jabami Yumeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{I may be new here, but I'd be happy to make friends with all of you.}Tuy mới đến nhưng mong mọi người giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{She's cuuute...}Dễ thương quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ehm...}Nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'd like for one of you to show Jabami-san around the academy.}Có ai dẫn Jabami tham quan trường không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzui-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{you're the class rep, right?}em là lớp trưởng nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can I count on you to do it?}Cô nhờ em nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzui-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{it's very nice to meet you.}rất vui được gặp cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{L-Likewise.}T-Tớ cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Something good happened since I became a house pet.}Lần đầu từ khi thành chó mình thấy vui thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wonderful...}Tuyệt quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{This academy is amazing.}Ngôi trường tuyệt quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad I transferred here.}Thật vui khi chuyển đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's this?}Cái đó là?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ehm, Jabami-san?}Jabami này.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes?}Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{Have you ever gambled before?}Cậu có chơi bài bạc không?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Gambled...?}Bài...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{You mean things like poker or mahjong?}Ý cậu là mấy thứ như xì tố hay mạt chược?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{I know the general idea of rules.}Tớ cũng biết sơ luật.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Gambling in this academy is almost like a tradition.}Cờ bạc là thứ truyền thống ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{After school hours}Sau giờ học,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{lots of places here turn into gamblnhiều ing dens.}nơi này sẽ biến thành sòng bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, there's a lot of rich kids here}Thế nên có nhiều đứa giàu có
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{with infinite amounts of money to gamble with.}đánh bạc với số tiền khổng lồ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{And soon they'll invite you to play...}Và chúng sẽ sớm mời cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{So be caref--}Thế nên cẩn--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well now...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{That sounds very fun.}Nghe thú vị thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Welcome to second year cherry blossom class!}Chào mừng đến với năm hai lớp anh đào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Where are you from?}Cậu từ đâu đến?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{What are you hobbies?}Sở thích là?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{What do you do on weekends?}Cậu làm gì vào cuối tuần?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Do you have a boyfriend?}Có bạn trai chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you!}Rất vui được gặp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you all as well.}Tớ cũng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hello!}Xin chào!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm Mary Saotome.}Tớ là Saotome Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you.}Rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Likewise, Saotome-san.}Tớ cũng vậy, Saotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Jabami-san, are you free after school?}Jabami, tí nữa có rảnh không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you are, would you like to play with me?}Nếu được chơi đánh bạc với tớ nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's happening?}Chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Looks like Mary-chan and transfer student are going to gamble.}Có vẻ Mary và học sinh mới sẽ đánh bạc với nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{What? Are they going to play that?}Sao? Thật á?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{What game should we play?}Chúng ta sẽ chơi gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{How about "Voting rock-paper-scissors"?}Chơi trò "Bốc bài kéo-búa-bao" nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's an original game we play in our class.}Là trò bọn tớ hay chơi trong lớp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{First, everyone in this class draw either a rock, paper or a scissor on a card.}Đầu tiên, mọi người sẽ vẽ những thẻ có kéo búa bao.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Then the cards go into that box so we can't see what's on them.}Sau đó sẽ được bỏ vào thùng kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Next we draw 3 cards from the box}Sau đó, ta lấy 3 thẻ từ hộp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{and choose one card to play.}và chọn thẻ để đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{If it's a tie, we pick a card from the remaining two and play again.}Nếu giống nhau thì ra bài tiếp và chơi lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{If 3 games are tie, that set is a draw. That's one set.}Nếu đến lần thứ 3 vẫn hòa thì kết thúc một hiệp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's not like a normal rock paper scissors, where you can just choose any move you want.}Nó không giống kéo búa bao thông thường vì cậu không thể ra tùy ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{Trying to read the flow of the game is the fun part.}Cố gắng đọc dòng chảy của trò chơi thú vị lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{That sounds fun! I definitely want to try it!}Nghe vui quá! Tớ phải thử thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's the spirit.}Phải thế chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ehm, Jabami-san...}Jabami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{Fido,}Chó ngoan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Go bring us some chips.}mua ít xèng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up.}Nhanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{These are chips.}Đây là xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Each one is 10000 yen.}Mỗi cái giá 10000 yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{For starters, I've got 120 chips for you.}Mỗi người bắt đầu với 120 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can choose how many chips we bet in each set, Jabami-san.}Cậu có thể cược thoải mái.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{The proof is in the pudding, so let's begin.}Không thử sao quen, bắt đầu nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's the bet?}Cậu cược bao nhiêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{All right then....}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's start with 2.}Bắt đầu bằng 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{In this game it's pretty rare to have 3 different cards in your hand.}Rất khó để được ba lá khác nhau khi bốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because you draw 3 cards, it's common to get double cards like 2 rocks and 1 paper.}Vì ngẫu nhiên nên có khi sẽ bốc trúng hai búa một bao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{For example if you've got 2 rocks}Ví dụ ta có hai búa,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{then it's possible that rock is the most common card in the box.}nhiều khả năng trong hộp sẽ có nhiều búa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Which means there's a high chance your opponent will play rock.}Tức là đối thủ cũng sẽ có thể có búa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{So you'd want to play paper.}Thế nên không được ra kéo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{You have to base your decision on this uncertainty.}Bạn phải dựa vào trực giác là chính.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{Have you decided?}Xong chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's show out cards together, on the signal.}Hãy đưa thẻ ra một lúc nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rock paper scissors!}Kéo búa bao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{You've got your first win, Jabami-san, congratulations.}Cậu thắng rồi, Jabami. Chúc mừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cám ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll take two of your chips then.}Tớ sẽ lấy hai xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, you've got the rules down, right?}Cậu hiểu luật rồi chứ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's keep going.}Bắt đầu nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes. Next we'll bet...}Ừm, tiếp theo là...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{50 chips.}50 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,50?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's 500000 yen. That escalated quickly.}Là 500000 yên? Đẩy nhanh quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're quite a gambler, Jabami-san.}Cậu là một con bạc nhỉ, Jabami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not really.}Không hẳn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:09:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{500000 yen on a single RPS game.}500000 yên trong một ván.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you ready?}Sẵn sàng chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rock... paper... scissors...}Kéo...búa...bao...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh, a tie.}Hòa à.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's play another card.}Lần nữa nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rock paper SCISSORS}Bao búa kéo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yay!}Hay quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{I win!}Tớ thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh...}Chà...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{I would've lost no matter what, huh?}Tớ cũng thua hiệp này luôn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad to have won such a big game.}Thật may khi tớ thắng ván này.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiếp theo là?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{go with 2.}2 xèng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let us begin.}Tớ lên đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rock paper scissors!}Kéo búa bao!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{The victory is yours, Jabami-san.}Cậu thắng Jabami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Contratulations.}Chúc mừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's next?}Tiếp theo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's bet 50 chips again.}Lại 50 nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're kidding me.}Đùa nhau à.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Did she forget the last time?}Cậu ta quên lần vừa nãy rồi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Interesting...}Thú vị đấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{I like that.}Tớ thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well then, let's go.}Lên luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rock paper scissors!}Kéo búa bao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Seems like we think alike.}Có vẻ chúng ta hợp nhau đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Next one...}Tiếp theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rock paper...}Kéo búa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{SCISSORS!}Bao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yay, seems like I win again!}Tớ lại thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll be taking this 500,000 yen.}Tớ sẽ lấn 500000 yên này.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{So far she's made 1,000,000 yen.}Cả triệu yên rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now, let's keep going.}Tiếp tục nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me you've got cold feet!}Đừng nói là sợ rồi nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can't say I blame you after losing 1,000,000 yen.}Mà thôi, thua cả triệu cơ mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not at all.}Không không.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{The game is just getting started.}Trò chơi chỉ mới bắt đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Next, let's bet 2 chips again.}Tiếp theo sẽ vẫn là 2 xèng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{She's finished...}Hết rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{One has 216 chips and one has 24.}24 đấu với 216.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{The gap is huge.}Khoảng cách quá lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{If she's scared when she's beaten and starts betting small, no way she can turn this around.}Nếu cậu ấy tỏ ra sợ hãi sẽ mất đi trực giác và không thể lật ngược.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, let's continue...}Vậy thì bắt đầu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rock paper scissors!}Kéo búa bao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Scissors.}Bao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, well, Jabami-san.}Chà chà, Jabami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Seems like you've lost all your chips.}Có vẻ cậu mất hết rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{She lost that much.}Thua nhiều quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{What a great game that was.}Màn ra mắt ấn tượng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Saotome-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Would you be up for one more game?}Chơi thêm một trận nữa nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't do it, Jabami-san.}Đừng, Jabami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{At this rate you'll become a house pet.}Nếu không cậu sẽ thành thú cưng đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Of course!}Dĩ nhiên!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's your bet?}Cậu cược gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{What a fool.}Đồ ngu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{She's digging her own grave.}Nó đang tự đào mồ chôn mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{How about 10,000,000 yen?}10 triệu yên nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{What the?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why do you carry that much cash?!}Tại sao cậu lại có nhiều thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't be an idiot!}Đừng có nói nhảm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{There's no way you can afford to bet that much on a single RPS game.}Không ai đi đặt cả món tiền đó vào một trò kéo búa bao cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're crazy!}Cậu bị điên à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{But isn't it what makes it fun?}Nhưng điều đó mới thú vị.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Madness is the essence of gambling, isn't it?}Điên cuồng là bản chất của cờ bạc mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Naturally, in the capitalist society money is life.}Trong cái xã hội chủ nghĩa này, tiền là tất cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{A sane person wouldn't entrust his life to luck.}Một lẽ dĩ nhiên, chả ai dựa vào may mắn cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{And yet a lot of people go to casinos.}Nhưng vẫn có nhiều kẻ đến sòng bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because people derive pleasure from this insanity.}Vì chúng sẽ tìm thấy niềm vui từ sự điên dại này.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{And so...}Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Gambling gets more fun the crazier it is!}Cờ bạc sẽ rất vui khi ta điên cuồng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{Shall we gamble?}Cùng chơi nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{President.}Chủ tịch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Today, a new student transferred to second year cherry blossom class.}Hôm nay có một học sinh chuyển trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{So...}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{We've got ourselves a snake in our paradise...}Một con rắn đã xuất hiện trong trường ta rồi nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{I-I won't follow you in something so stupid.}Cậu nói gì tôi chả hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me you've got cold feet.}Đừng nói là cậu sợ nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{This idiot girl...}Con khốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{is making fun of me!}lấy mình ra làm trò đùa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{What is she...}Cậu ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{She just transferred in and got involved in such a reckless game.}chỉ vừa chuyển trường mà lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{How can she stay so calm?}Làm sao có thể bình tĩnh như thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{HIgh stakes game are so exciting, right?}Cược càng cao chơi càng đã nhỉ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Does she even realize that 10,000,000 yen is on the line?}Cô ta sử dụng tới 10 triệu mà vẫn bình thản thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, whatever.}Mà sao cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna win, because...}Mình sẽ thắng...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{21 voters out of 30 are voting to give me an advantage.}21/30 người ở đây đều theo phe mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{They all have different reasons for it, like increasing their social status...}Chúng đều muốn gia tăng địa vị...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Regardless, those 21 "slaves" will vote how I tell them.}Thế nên 21 nô lệ sẽ theo phe mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{This time rocks and papers}Lần này là Búa và Bao,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{should be the most common.}sẽ chiếm ưu thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{There should be hardly any scissors.}Kéo sẽ không còn nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Chances that Jabami would get them are low.}Cơ hội để Jabami thắng là rất thấp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{So if I play the paper I won't lose.}Nếu mình ra bao sẽ không thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{The problem would be if I don't get paper.}Vấn đề là nếu mình không có bao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Two papers! Almost ideal!}Hai bao! Ngon rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've won! This ends now!}Mình sẽ thắng! Kết thúc nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you ready?}Sẵn sàng chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{Shall we begin?}Ta bắt đầu nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{You've only got 3 cards, not much you can do even if you take it slow.}Cậu chỉ có 3 lá thôi nên khỏi do dự nữa đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Did you think I wouldn't notice?}Tưởng tôi không nhận ra à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{Everyone is working for you, Saotome-san, right?}Mọi người đều đang hỗ trợ Saotome nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Although based on the results, not all of them are voting your way.}Dựa vào kết quả, có vẻ không phải tất cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{10 people... or maybe 20 to ensure your victory.}10...không 20 người cho cậu sẽ thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{How dare y--}Sao mày dám--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{You didn't do a good job hiding it.}Cậu giấu diếm tệ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{In two games where you bet 500,000 yen,}Trong hai ván tớ cược 500000 yên,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{you played the same cards both times.}cậu đã ra 3 thẻ giống nhau ở cả hai ván.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{So it's natural for me to think that you were up to something.}Thế nên tớ nghĩ chắc chắn có gì đó không đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{When we weren't betting much, you mixed you cards well.}Khi không cược cao, cậu đã trộn thẻ của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's was a bad attempt to hide it.}Giả ngu khá tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can't fool anyone if you're not prepared to lose money.}Cậu không thể lừa ai đó nếu chưa từng bị lừa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{Would you stop with your weird smack talk?}Dừng mấy trò nói nhảm lại được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you intend to end the game--}Nếu muốn kết thúc--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, no, no.}Không, không, không.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't dream of it.}Phí lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because...}Vì...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{The it's going to get much more fun from now on.}Từ giờ mới thú vị mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{How the hell can she be so calm.}Sao nó tỏ ra bình thản thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is she that confident that she's gonna win?}Không lẽ nó chắc thắng?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nah, that's not possible.}Không thể nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{She can't be sure of victory without knowing what I'll play.}Làm sao có thể thắng khi không biết mình ra lá nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's a bluff.}Chỉ là trò lừa gạt thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{If I play paper now, I'll win!}Nếu mình cứ ra bao sẽ thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Done with your speech?}Nói xong chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{If so, why don't you decide what card to play now?}Rồi thì ra bài đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't say I didn't warn you.}Tôi đã cảnh cáo rồi đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you done?}Xong chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's begin!}Bắt đầu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rock paper SCIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIISSORS}Kéo búa baaaaaao!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Scissors.}Kéo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Scissors?}Kéo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{No way, can't be...}Không thể nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{It sure can.}Có thể chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can see it with your own eyes.}Cậu có thể nhìn bằng mắt mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now then, let's talk about winnings.}Giờ thì, hãy nói về chiến thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not counting the money I lost, I get 8,800,000 yen.}Trừ vào tiền tớ thua vừa nãy thì cậu đang nợ 8 triệu 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{Be so kind and pay up, please.}Xin hãy trả đủ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why did this happen...?}Tại sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{I wanted to put her into a debt,}Mình chỉ muốn đặt nó vào một khoản nợ,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{why did I end up losing 8,800,000 yen instead?}tại sao cuối cùng lại thua 8 triệu 8?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{What in the world...}Vậy là sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Who the hell is this girl?}Con nhỏ này là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{Would you be so kind as to pay up?}Nhớ trả nợ đầy đủ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{N-no...}K-Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Come again?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't have it right now...}Bây giờ tôi không có...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Could I possibly ask you to wait a few days?}Xin hãy chờ vài ngày được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Saotome...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Today was very fun so I'll consider it paid.}Hôm nay tớ đang vui nên sẽ xem xét lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Have a nice day, everyone.}Mọi người, một ngày tốt lành.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{I hope you'll treat me as an equal starting tomorrow.}Hi vọng ngày mai cậu sẽ đối xử tốt với tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Something wrong?}Có chuyện gì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.02,0:18:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want to ask you something.}Tớ có chuyện muốn hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{How did you figure it all out?}Làm sao cậu biết được những chuyện xảy ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's easy.}Quá dễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{From the start I knew that Saotome-san was manipulating votes.}Ngay từ đầu tớ đã biết cậu ta mua phiếu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{So I only needed to know what card would be the most common.}Thế nên chỉ cần kiểm tra xem thẻ nào chiếm đa số.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{But how?}Nhưng bằng cách nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's say that Saotome-san had 20 people in her pocket.}Cho rằng có khoảng 20 người theo phe Saotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{She needed to get them to vote for the same card or it wouldn't work.}Cậu ta cần họ vẽ thẻ giống nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{But as far as I could tell there was no pattern to the votes.}Nhưng theo tớ quan sát, thì có vẻ không phải thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{On the other hand having to remember a particular order of the voted cards would be difficult.}Vì để nhớ hết số lượng từng thẻ rất khó khăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{So they must be deciding what to vote for on the stop.}Thế nên tớ đoán là lúc gần cuối mới quyết định.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{But how?}Vậy bằng cách nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{While using my chips I observed Saotome-san}Khi sử dụng xèng, tớ đã quan sát Saotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{but she didn't sign her followers whatsoever.}Nhưng cậu ta chẳng ra hiệu gì cho những người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{So was it a sound?}Thế thì âm thanh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{No...}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{It wasn't it.}Không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{This means that there could be only one way to do so.}Tức là chỉ còn lại một.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Instead of Saotome-san, someone else was giving a signal to the class.}Thay vì Saotome, ai đó trong lớp đã truyền tín hiệu cho Saotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{If this is true then there had to be a person in class that her helpers would look at.}Nếu đúng thì chắc chắn có một người đứng sau nhìn bài tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{I was watching but the I realized something.}Tớ đã quan sát và nhận ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{I thought it was natural that people would stare at me}Cứ tưởng mọi người nhìn tớ chằm chằm là điều dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{but that was where I was making my mistake.}Nhưng lúc đó tớ đã sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{They weren't staring at me...}Họ không nhìn chằm chằm vào tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{In truth, they were staring at the person behind me.}Mà là người phía sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{You figured that out too, huh?}Cậu đã biết đến đó cơ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{The rest was easy.}Phần còn lại quá dễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Only thing I had to do is guess the sign based on your actions.}Tớ chỉ cần đoán xem hành động của cậu là gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{My actions? But I was behind you.}Của tớ? Nhưng tớ ở sau cậu mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{As you know, a hand mirror is essential for any girl.}Cô gái nào chả có gương chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{I see...}Vậy à...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can I ask you one more thing?}Tớ hỏi cậu một điều nữa nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{How did you managed to pull scissors in the last round?}Làm sao cậu có thể lấy hết kéo ở vòng cuối?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tớ nghĩ nó phải ít lắm chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah... That was a complete coincidence.}À...trùng hợp thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{I was lucky!}Tớ may mắn mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{No way!}Đùa à!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{You used 1,200,000 yen to find the truth.}Cậu dùng 1 triệu 2 để tìm sự thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{And you mean that you bet 10,000,000 and relied on luck to win?}Và dùng 10 triệu cho may mắn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thinking about it, there was no point in telling everyone about the trick--}Nghĩ về nó, không có cách nào để nói về thủ thuật--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{you could've won more games with this knowledge.}Cậu không thể thắng nhiều hơn chỉ dựa vào nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yet you did this...}Tức là cậu làm điều này...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{because you enjoy taking risks.}vì thích mạo hiểm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Taking risk on its own is pretty boring.}Chỉ mạo hiểm không thì quá chán.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{But having big advantage is boring too, you know?}Nhưng áp đảo quá cũng chán nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{You certainly are special.}Cậu đúng là đặc biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've never felt that way.}Tớ chưa bao giờ nghĩ theo cách đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm going to drop out of this academy.}Chắc tớ nghỉ luôn đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{I had a big debt.}Tớ nợ một khoản lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{I owed 5,000,000 to Saotome Mary.}Khoảng 5 triệu từ Saotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{I tried to make some money by gambling but my debt just got bigger and bigger.}Tớ thử kiếm ít tiền trong cờ bạc và ngày càng nợ nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Like I was swimming trough a swamp.}Cứ như bơi trong vũng lầy vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{I give up}Tớ mệt rồi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{If I had your strength, I'm sure things would've turned out differently.}nếu mạnh như cậu chắc tớ sẽ khác nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm truly sorry.}Tớ rất xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{That reminds me, I want you to have it as thanks.}Nhắc mới nhớ, tớ phải cám ơn cậu nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please.}Nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Today I had a fun time gambling.}Hôm nay tớ đã rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{This isn't much to express the my feelings, but please take it.}Đây là tấm lòng của tớ, nên hãy nhận đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{N-no.}K-Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{I was a part of the scheme, I can't take this.}Tớ không thể nhận nó--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{I dislike situations where I know for sure if I'm going to win or lose.}Tớ ghét cảm giác thắng chắc hay thua chắc lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.58,0:22:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because it's not really gambling.}Vì đó không phải cờ bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thanks to you, I was able to play a fun and stimulating game today.}Nhờ cậu mà tớ có thể vui vẻ và kích thích đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.92,0:22:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much.}Cám ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.42,0:22:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{I was able to see her smile quite clearly.}Mình có thể nhìn rõ nụ cười ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{There was no pity or resentment towards me.}Không có lòng thương hại hay oán giận với mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{She just wanted to thank me because she was able to enjoy the game today.}Cậu ấy chỉ cám ơn vì mình đã làm cho cậu ấy vui vẻ hôm nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{She's not a normal girl.}Một người kì lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{She's a gambling enthusiast...}Con nghiện cờ bạc...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{A compulsive gambler.}Một Kakegurui.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
